{"tid":428571,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史遺物] Nikon FG-20 菲林機","createTime":"2017-10-08T07:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T00:44:39.000Z","uid":72923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0e204a245d279a377d48bd48a77fcadfd0a9bdb2","tid":428571,"uid":72923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3r0zgc15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3r0zgc15&h=3fb6a1fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近小弟想玩菲林機，老豆又醒起有部。<br />\n<br />\n佢只知道壞左但唔知壞咩，機入面又有啲塵，鏡都發左霉。<br />\n<br />\n會問問整唔整翻好(整又幾錢左右，定買過部。。<br />\n<br />\n小弟係新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩都唔太識，求Ching賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7910181c0d3d2b80ba0832633842e504126a7daf","tid":428571,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:26:37.000Z","msg":"tamron鏡not bad, 個mount都值d錢"},{"pid":"b7f4dafd247da08d413252ed07c7be49a4615fbe","tid":428571,"uid":14535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/3r0zgc15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3r0zgc15&h=3fb6a1fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近小弟想玩菲林機，老豆又醒起有部。<br />\n<br />\n佢只知道壞左但唔知壞咩，機入面又有啲塵，鏡都發左霉。<br />\n<br />\n會問問整唔整翻好(整又幾錢左右，定買過部。。<br />\n<br />\n小弟係新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩都唔太識，求Ching賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nkeep得好唔好? 鏡有無發霉起霧之類?<br />\n識唔識操控部相機? 最基本其實就過片 快門速度 快門釋放<br />\n你自己試下部機正唔正常過到片, 快門郁唔郁 反光板正唔正常 去check下有咩問題~<br />\n<br />\n如果大壞要整 整一整三兩百都走唔甩, 我見Ebay一部都係300左右(無睇清楚 應該正常 work) 加埋運都係400左右<br />\n除非部機有好深意義, 如果唔係你問人人地應該都係會叫你買過部好過~<br />\n<br />\n自己確定左有咩壞先, 再講你知邊度有得整"},{"pid":"865d45138b694371bd01885b2e775d39fe438c0a","tid":428571,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T21:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/3r0zgc15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3r0zgc15&h=3fb6a1fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近小弟想玩菲林機，老豆又醒起有部。<br />\n<br />\n佢只知道壞左但唔知壞咩，機入面又有啲塵，鏡都發左霉。<br />\n<br />\n會問問整唔整翻好(整又幾錢左右，定買過部。。<br />\n<br />\n小弟係新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩都唔太識，求Ching賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無入新電試...?"},{"pid":"700d31fdbcb1166e2b25c8a7a01a9f3c9a160da4","tid":428571,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T22:35:25.000Z","msg":"FG-20 機就一般真係三幾百就有<br />\n巴打呢部黑色比較少有啲<br />\n如果想整嘅話香港應該冇乜師傅會整<br />\n不過可以試下去西環(地址冇係手一陣覆)<br />\n價錢大概同部機差唔多<br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣玩不如買多個FM 或者FE, 筆直鬆啲就FA 機身用啲鏡去影啦"},{"pid":"9fbf4caf24b3b729e7c2b67e0541872ac5dd6b6a","tid":428571,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:19:39.000Z","msg":"德輔道西, 屈地街口有間電器行叫天達<br />\n老闆以前係Nikon 嘅師傅黎<br />\nFG-20機身嘅問題可以問下佢先"},{"pid":"39e38e6a8bd8e59c16aa8895c3e523870003f1db","tid":428571,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:44:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}